text: Move-in ready with so much potential to make your own. This home features original hardwood flooring and a floor plan with a seamless flow, ample natural light and a refreshing cross-breeze. Recent updates include upgraded electrical within the past four years, a new water heater installed in 2019, a new washer and an updated roof for added peace of mind. The two back bedrooms offer serene views of the lush garden, providing a tranquil atmosphere to wake up to or enjoy while working from home. Outside, the private backyard is a true oasis, featuring low-maintenance landscaping and an impressive variety of fruit trees, including pomegranates, blood oranges, bananas, grapes, peaches and more. The upper California Native garden is low maintenance, sustainable and water-conscious. The cozy back porch area is perfect for relaxing and enjoying this peaceful retreat. Located near the expansive Chollas Lake Park, one of the largest parks in San Diego County, and with convenient access to Downtown San Diego, SDSU, the airport as well as the 15, 805, and 94 freeways. This home offers both natural beauty and prime accessibility. Come see today!

This is a fantastic opportunity for both seasoned investors and those looking to enter the multi-family market. Dont miss your chance to capitalize on this profitable venture!
